; マップを開いた時に必ず実行されるスクリプト
[initial]

if(! loading) events.push2(2, 3, 4);

[endinitial]
;===============================================================================
;◆イベント◆

; 初期発生イベント
events = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7]

;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*event_1
;[exp] party.lastIsMove || inSearching

[if exp='! o.精霊の力を宿す石.accepted']
	@fg c=9009 left=450 top=0
	[texton]
	There is a large rock emitting beautiful light. What could this be?[k]
	[textoff]
	@clf
	[eventoff]
[endif]

[if exp='o.精霊の力を宿す石.completed || game.findItem(o.精霊の石) !== void']
	@fg c=9009 left=450 top=0
	[texton]
	There is a spirit rock. I don't think I need any more spirit stones.[k]
	[textoff]
	@clf
	[eventoff]
[endif]

@fg c=9009 left=450 top=0
@wait time=500

[texton]
In the center of the hall was a large rock formation that emitted a beautiful light.[k]
[if exp='game.isFreeMode']
	Could this be the spirit stone the client was talking about?[k]
[else]
	[テオ f=05]「Could this be the Spirit Stone...?」[k]
[endif]
For now, if all we need to do is satisfy the client's request, then we should just bring back a piece of the rock.[k]
With that in mind, I reached out my hand toward the rock. Then [――――][k]
[textoff]

@playse storage=magic6 loop=true
@image layer=e0 storage=screen_blue left=0 top=0
@anime_fadein layer=e0
@image layer=e1 storage=PE_base_view visible=true left=0 top=0 mode=psdogde5
@startemit layer=e1 storage=PE_energy time=-1
@wait time=5000

[texton]
[if exp='game.isFreeMode']
	...![k]
[else]
	[テオ f=05]「...!」[k]
[endif]
Numerous balls of light gathered from the surrounding area! What on earth is going on?[k]
[textoff]

@playse storage=shakin4
@flash on=1000
@layopt layer=e0 visible=false
@clearemit layer=e1
@fgf c=slime_great left=450 top=-90
@flash off=1000
@wait time=1000

[texton]
[name n=Slime]「...」[k]
[if exp='game.isFreeMode']
	Suddenly, a giant slime appeared right in front of me![k]
[else]
	[テオ f=12]「What, a giant slime?!」[k]
[endif]
[textoff]
@clf

@monster pos=3 name=グレートスライム
@callbattle escape=false bgm=boss

@fgf c=9009 left=450 top=0
[texton]
[if exp='game.isFreeMode']
	After defeating the giant slime, we breathed a sigh of relief.[k]
	Perhaps it was a guardian deity trying to protect the spirit rock.[k]
	We cut off a small piece of the spirit rock to take with us.[k]
[else]
	[テオ f=10]「Phew, that was a surprise.」[k]
	Perhaps it was a guardian deity trying to protect the spirit rock.[k]
	We cut off a small piece of the spirit rock to take with us.[k]
[endif]
[textoff]
@getitem item=精霊の石
@clf

[eventoff]
